Security Groups Rules:
Component              Port         Protocol   Source                          Reason
ALB Security Group     80,443       TCP        0.0.0.0/0                       Allow public HTTP & HTTPS traffic
Frontend ECS SG        3000,443     TCP        ALB Security Group              Restricts access to ALB only
Backend ECS SG         5000         TCP        Frontend ECS Security Group     Allow only Frontend ECS access
RDS Security Group     3306         TCP        Backend ECS Security Group      Limits access to Backend ECS only 
SSH                    22           TCP        Your IP                         Only allow SSH from trusted admin IPs

